title: La Trattoria
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Italian restaurant in Key West. Vegan choices include bruschetta, the insalata paesana with figs, red onions, apples in a balsamic vinaigrette, and pastas. Will use vegan pasta and make several of the sauces to order, omitting cheese and cream, such as the aglio e olio and the spaghetti Norma, with a fresh basil, garlic, tomato, and eggplant sauce.
